    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 和全球 IT 中断的解释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-microsoft-it-outage-what-caused-it-what-comes-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[7 月 19 日星期五，CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 发生大规模 IT 故障，导致航班停飞、市场混乱、全球企业陷入混乱。CrowdStrike 股价一度下跌 15%。此次中断的影响预计将持续数天，而微软 Azure 云服务的一个看似无关的问题加剧了此次中断的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-microsoft-it-outage-what-caused-it-what-comes-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
